This is chat bot multiple file program execution:

This is an make file program

make command is used build the program 

make will build the binary file and convert the .c file to .o file 

after make command run the server by this command ./udp_chatbot_server 127.0.0.1 8080

then run the client one by uing the command ./udp_chatbot_client 127.0.0.1 8080

make clean is used to clear the binary files
